modName: Masters of the Universe Prince Adam outfit
summary: a simple retexture of one the outfits, and the hide boots..
descriptionHtml:
for all Masters of the Universe fans... heres Prince Adam\'s outfit via Skyrim...

this retexture was made purely for fun,.. im a big Masters fan and this particular outfit kept reminding me of Adams look,...

2 things that may be off putting are; bandits will be walking around in purple boots; and this particular outfit shares the pants with another outfit- so, that one will have pink pants too!

again, this is just for fun, and once the ck is released, this can be its own instead of a replacement
